ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectOrder No. 151 - (Quebec) Provincial Emergencies Financial Assistance Order
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER N° 151 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the federal government to provide financial assistance to the province of QUEBEC with respect to the FLOODING that affected the province, from March 18 to June 29, 2011.
